     FGHCPL29 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@MHN1  5
     C                     PARM           P@MHN2  5
     C                     PARM           P@MHN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@KSEQ  2
     C                     PARM           P@SETI  9
